Detailed Description

This package contains classes that process ecore models to be easily parsed by MATLAB.

The hierarchical model is translated into a flat list, with elements ordered in such a way that they can added by MATLAB sequentially.

Some information relevant to Simulink is added as well: the position and a full path name. The entry point is ModelProcessor.
